{"tid":1058383,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"賣不動！2月中國手機出貨量慘跌19.9％ 創3年新低","createTime":"2019-03-12T13:28:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-12T15:37:25.000Z","uid":54733,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"114fff64fa012fb39880b1f584e781439b2c72c6","tid":1058383,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T13:28:06.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國工信部所屬中國信通院今（12）日發布2月中國國內手機市場分析報告，總體年增率慘跌19.9％，創3年來新低。<br />\n<br />\n《鉅亨網》援引中國信通院數據指出，中國今年2月份整體手機出貨量為1451.1萬支，年增率慘跌19.9％，其中4G手機1398.4萬支占96.4％，年增率下降20.2％。若計入今年1月份，整體出貨量共為4855.9萬支，年增率下滑15.1％。<br />\n<br />\n中國《界面新聞》指出，以歷史數據而論，2月一向是中國手機出貨量的低點，但專家分析指出，總體而言中國國內手機市場已經明顯飽和，在5G、折疊螢幕等消費者期待的新技術上市並普及前，成長空間非常有限。<br />\n<br />\n今年初中國共上市73款新機，以款式來說，年減率42.1％，顯示出手機製造商也採取保守的策略，同樣觀望著新技術帶來的供需關係發展。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2724711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2724711&d=fcvOs274DMK6OEArnk0LaxPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=87fc429f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2724711&h=1bb03d96\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2724711</a>"},{"pid":"86e1ea64a6ea0be2bcb24641f0a24602325b4607","tid":1058383,"uid":44171,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T13:36:27.000Z","msg":"部部機都只可以裝果幾個app, 換黎都無意慾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05fa6ce0532e9657ef26b0f0121993fc72af0f20","tid":1058383,"uid":511,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T14:30:28.000Z","msg":"農曆新年假呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"084a56accf6e0aceae93e0017abc6b70651e038f","tid":1058383,"uid":171192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T14:34:32.000Z","msg":"又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"